s://people.com/music/gustavo-dudamel-conducting-vienna-philharmonic-new-years-celebration/ |accessdate=2020-12-10 |work=People |date=December 30, 2016 11:00 AM |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112195626/https://people.com/music/gustavo-dudamel-conducting-vienna-philharmonic-new-years-celebration/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年诺贝尔音乐会，杜達美指挥[[皇家斯德哥尔摩爱乐乐团|皇家斯德哥尔摩爱乐乐团]]（Royal Stockholm Philharmonic Orchestra）演奏莫扎特[[第41號交響曲_(莫札特)|第41號交響曲]]和[[理查·史特勞斯|史特勞斯]]的《[[查拉圖斯特拉如是說_(史特勞斯)|查拉圖斯特拉如是說]]》。<ref>{{cite news |author1=Gustavo Dudamel |title=NOBEL: Gustavo Dudamel leads 2017 Nobel Prize Concert |url=https://www.gustavodudamel.com/us-en/nobel-gustavo-dudamel-leads-2017-nobel-prize-concert |accessdate=2020-12-12 |work=Gustavo Dudamel |date=21 APRIL 2017 |archive-date=2019-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190711134807/https://www.gustavodudamel.com/us-en/nobel-gustavo-dudamel-leads-2017-nobel-prize-concert |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2018年，杜達美指挥[[洛杉矶爱乐乐团|洛杉矶爱乐乐团]]演出包括《[[弥撒（伯恩斯坦）|弥撒]]》（Mass）和《[[齊徹斯特詩篇（伯恩斯坦）|齊徹斯特詩篇]]》（Chichester Psalms）以庆祝[[李奧納德·伯恩斯坦|伯恩斯坦]]的一百年诞辰。<ref>{{cite news |author1=LA Phil |title=LA Phil Announces Cast for Bernstein's Mass, Conducted by Gustavo Dudamel |url=https://www.laphil.com/press/releases/1678 |accessdate=2020-12-13 |work=LA Phil |date=2017-12-07 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129230402/https://www.laphil.com/press/releases/1678 |dead-url=no }}</ref>同年12月，杜達美在[[大都会歌剧院|大都会歌剧院]]首演[[朱塞佩·威爾第|威爾第]]的歌剧《[[奧泰羅|奧泰羅]]》。<ref>{{cite news |author1=The Metropolitan Opera |title=Gustavo Dudamel makes his Metropolitan Opera debut conducting Verdi’s Otello on December 14 |url=https://www.metopera.org/about/press-releases/gustavo-dudamel-makes-his-metropolitan-opera-debut-conducting-verdis-otello-on-december-14/ |accessdate=2020-12-13 |work=The Metropolitan Opera |date=2018-11-12 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126045617/https://www.metopera.org/about/press-releases/gustavo-dudamel-makes-his-metropolitan-opera-debut-conducting-verdis-otello-on-december-14/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2019年10月24日，杜達美与前两任洛杉矶爱乐乐团的音乐总监[[祖賓·梅塔|祖賓·梅塔]]和[[埃薩-佩卡·薩洛寧|埃薩-佩卡·薩洛寧]]合作指挥该乐团的一百年诞辰音乐会，其中杜達美指挥《[[火鳥_(芭蕾舞)|火鳥 (芭蕾舞)]]》并首演[[丹尼尔·比亚尔纳松|比亚尔纳松]]为该三位指挥家所作的《[[我从太空中看地球上的三个指挥家|我从太空中看地球上的三个指挥家]]》。<ref>{{cite news |author1=LA Phil |title=Centennial Birthday Celebration Concert & Gala |url=https://www.laphil.com/events/performances/644/2019-10-24/centennial-birthday-celebration-concert-gala |accessdate=2020-12-13 |work=LA Phil |date=THU / OCT 24, 2019 - 7:00PM |archive-date=2020-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918173602/https://www.laphil.com/events/performances/644/2019-10-24/centennial-birthday-celebration-concert-gala |dead-url=no }}</ref>

杜達美在2020年一月份续签作为[[洛杉矶爱乐乐团|洛杉矶爱乐乐团]]音乐总监的合同直到2025-2026年。<ref>{{cite news |author1=Jessica Gelt |title=Gustavo Dudamel extends L.A. Phil contract to 2025-26 |url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/story/2020-01-15/gustavo-dudamel-renews-la-phil-contract |accessdate=2020-12-13 |work=LA Times |date=2020-01-15 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225051345/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/story/2020-01-15/gustavo-dudamel-renews-la-phil-contract |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 个人生活 ==
杜达美至今共有两次婚姻。第一次于2006年，杜達美在[[卡拉卡斯|卡拉卡斯]]与委内瑞拉是舞者和记者的[[伊洛伊萨·马图伦|伊洛伊萨·马图伦]]（Eloísa Maturén）结婚，并于2011年4月1日在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]诞下一子，名叫马丁·杜达梅尔（Martin Dudamel Maturen）。<ref>{{cite news |author1=LOS ANGELES (CBS) |title=LA Phil’s Gustavo Dudamel, Wife Welcome First Child |url=https://losangeles.cbslocal.com/2011/04/02/la-phils-gustavo-dudamel-wife-welcome-first-child/ |accessdate=2020-11-12 |work=CBS Local Media |date=April 2, 2011 at 2:58 pm |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123100241/https://losangeles.cbslocal.com/2011/04/02/la-phils-gustavo-dudamel-wife-welcome-first-child/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年，杜達美向[[洛杉矶县高级法院|洛杉矶县高级法院]]递交了离婚申请，此前两人已经分居。<ref>{{cite news |author1=DAVID NG |title=L.A. Philharmonic conductor Gustavo Dudamel and wife file for divorce |url=https://www.baltimoresun.com/la-et-cm-gustavo-dudamel-eloise-divorce-20150319-story.html |accessdate=2020-11-12 |work=The Baltimore Sun |date=MAR 19, 2015 AT 5:30 PM}}</ref>他於2017年與西班牙女演員[[瑪莉亞·瓦維德|瑪莉亞·瓦維德]]結婚，目前这是他的第二次婚姻。<ref>{{cite news |author1=Norman Lebrecht |title=WORD’S OUT: DUDAMEL GOT MARRIED |url=https://slippedisc.com/2017/05/words-out-dudamel-got-married/ |accessdate=2020-11-10 |work=Slippedisc |date=May 7, 2017 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116160556/https://slippedisc.com/2017/05/words-out-dudamel-got-married/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

